ing: 2 (0.3 ounce) packages sugar-free lemon flavored Jell-OÂ® mix
1 (8 ounce) container lite frozen whipped topping, thawed
des: "Low-fat cottage cheese is mixed with Cool Whip LiteÂ® and dry sugar-free gelatin to create a delightful dessert. You can use any flavor Jell-O; I prefer lemon or orange."
ins: Place the cottage cheese in a food processor and blend until creamy. Whisk in the flavored gelatin powder, then fold in the thawed whipped topping. Refrigerate until serving.
